e:T7bc,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Process Street better than Slack Workflows?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Process Street scores 7.0 overall while Slack Workflows scores 6.0. Process Street is best for operations teams and onboarding, while Slack Workflows excels for Slack teams and internal processes."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Process Street or Slack Workflows?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Process Street starts at $100/mo and Slack Workflows starts at Free.  Slack Workflows offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Process Street to Slack Workflows?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Process Street and Slack Workflows support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Process Street vs Slack Workflows?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Process Street holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10. Slack Workflows has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Process Street for excellent for documenting and running processes and Slack Workflows for built into slack—zero extra cost."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Process Street or Slack Workflows?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Process Street for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Slack Workflows remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize built into slack—zero extra cost. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",