13:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Process Street and Slack Workflows share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. Interestingly, both platforms offer nearly identical feature sets. The difference lies more in the implementation quality and depth of each feature rather than feature availability itself. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Process Street holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Slack Workflows scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
14:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Slack Workflows comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Process Street begins at $100/mo. Slack Workflows stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Process Street requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
